 TO TRIGGER TOOL]\\\". Verify the tool execution in the logs.\\n```\\n\\n### Risks / Red Flags\\n- **Dependency Hell:** Adding tools often brings new library dependencies. Ensure Claude updates `requirements.txt` or the environment setup.\\n- **Tool Overlap:** Before adding a new tool, we must verify it doesn't overlap with existing capabilities like `google_search` or `read_context_doc`.\\n\\n### Action Checklist\\n1. [ ] **Identify the Tool:** Which V2 tool are we building first? (e.g., the MCP Google Docs reader or the Skill Registry connector?)\\n2. [ ] **Define the Contract:** Update `DATA_CONTRACT.md` with the tool's input/output shape.\\n3. [ ] **Execute Prompt:** Pass the surgical prompt above to Claude Code.\\n\\n**Which tool from the V2 roadmap should we point this at first?** I'm ready to refine this prompt for the specific MCP or RAG integration we discussed.\"}],\"role\":\"model\"},\"intermediate_data\":{\"tool_uses\":[{\"id\":\"adk-db3bd997-3e43-410b-b4c7-8b200c957e03\",\"args\":{\"skill_name\":\"SESSION_MEMORY_SKILL\"},\"name\":\"invoke_skill\"},{\"id\":\"adk-fc27df60-96be-4eda-857d-4e7ca061a181\",\"args\":{\"days\":7},\"name\":\"read_session_memory\"}],\"intermediate_responses\":[]},\"creation_timestamp\":0.0},\"expected_invocation\":{\"invocation_id\":\"inv_prompt_01\",\"user_content\":{\"parts\":[{\"video_metadata\":null,\"thought\":null,\"inline_data\":null,\"file_data\":null,\"thought_signature\":null,\"code_execution_result\":null,\"executable_code\":null,\"function_call\":null,\"function_response\":null,\"text\":\"Write a prompt for Claude Code to add a new tool\"}],\"role\":\"user\"},\"final_response\":{\"parts\":[{\"video_metadata\":null,\"thought\":null,\"inline_data\":null,\"file_data\":null,\"thought_signature\":null,\"code_execution_result\":null,\"executable_code\":null,\"function_call\":null,\"function_response\":null,\"text\":\"\"}],\"role\":\"model\"},\"intermediate_data\":{\"tool_uses\":[{\"id\":null,\"args\":{},\"name\":\"get_curren